briefdescription.para: The amount of frames to delay OnAppAboutToStart after the applauncher reports to be ready. Defaults to 5, should be enough to ensure all flight and scenario modules are loaded. Increase if necessary.
Is the App window visible on the screen
Called when the app is disabled from an external source (e.g., leaving an appscene where the app/button is visible)
Called when the app is enabled from an external source (e.g., entering an appscene where the app/button is visible)
Called when the app button is toggled off (by clicking)
Called whenever the cursor enters the button (or app's) hover area
Called whenever the cursor leaves the button (or app's) hover area
Called when the applauncher iself is disabled (e.g., leaving game scenes where the app launched existed)
Called when the applauncher iself is enabled (e.g., entering game scenes where the app launched exists)
Called when the app button is toggled on (by clicking)
